<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Sprintf on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/sprintf/</link><description>Recent content in Sprintf on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/sprintf/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] C sprintf() Deprecated — Replace with snprintf()</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/deprecated/c/sprintf/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/deprecated/c/sprintf/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="solution-c-sprintf-deprecated--replace-with-snprintf"&gt;[Solution] C sprintf() Deprecated — Replace with snprintf()&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;sprintf()&lt;/code&gt; function is deprecated in modern C because it writes to a buffer without any bounds checking. If the formatted output exceeds the destination buffer size, it overflows into adjacent memory. The safe replacement is &lt;code&gt;snprintf()&lt;/code&gt;, which takes an explicit size parameter and truncates or returns the required length.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="what-youll-see"&gt;What You&amp;rsquo;ll See&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Compiling with &lt;code&gt;_CRT_SECURE_NO_WARNINGS&lt;/code&gt; not defined on MSVC, or with security-focused compiler flags:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>PHP Warning: sprintf(): Too few arguments</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/php/warning-in-sprintf/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/php/warning-in-sprintf/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="php-warning-sprintf-too-few-arguments"&gt;PHP Warning: sprintf(): Too few arguments&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This warning occurs when &lt;code&gt;sprintf()&lt;/code&gt; has more placeholders in the format string than arguments provided. Each &lt;code&gt;%&lt;/code&gt; placeholder requires a corresponding argument.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adding format placeholders without providing matching arguments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Removing arguments after updating the format string&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dynamic format strings where placeholders vary&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="match-placeholders-to-arguments"&gt;Match Placeholders to Arguments&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-php" data-lang="php"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;php&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong — two placeholders, one argument
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;sprintf&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello %s, today is %s&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct — two placeholders, two arguments
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;sprintf&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello %s, today is %s&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Monday&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;?&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="count-placeholders-dynamically"&gt;Count Placeholders Dynamically&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-php" data-lang="php"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;php&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;safeSprintf&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt; $format, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;mixed&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;...&lt;/span&gt;$args)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; $placeholderCount &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;substr_count&lt;/span&gt;($format, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;%&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;substr_count&lt;/span&gt;($format, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;%%&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; ($placeholderCount &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;count&lt;/span&gt;($args)) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;throw&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;\InvalidArgumentException&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Too few arguments for format string&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;sprintf&lt;/span&gt;($format, &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;...&lt;/span&gt;$args);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;?&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="use-named-placeholders"&gt;Use Named Placeholders&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-php" data-lang="php"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;php&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Use explicit argument positioning
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;sprintf&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello %1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;$s&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;, you have %2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;$d&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt; messages&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;?&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-php" data-lang="php"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;php&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// This triggers the warning
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;sprintf&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Name: %s, Age: %d, City: %s&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;30&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Warning: sprintf(): Too few arguments
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;sprintf&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Name: %s, Age: %d, City: %s&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;30&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;NYC&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;?&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
